'''板齿鼠'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Bandicota indica''}}）为[[鼠科|鼠科]][[板齿鼠属|板齿鼠属]]的动物，原生于[[中国|中国]]、[[印度|印度]]、[[印尼|印尼]]、[[老挝|老挝]]、[[缅甸|缅甸]]、[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]]、[[斯里兰卡|斯里兰卡]]、[[泰国|泰国]]、[[越南|越南]]，并引进[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]<ref name=iucn/>。分布于[[中国|中国]]的[[广西|广西]]、[[广东|广东]]、[[云南|云南]]、[[四川|四川]]、[[贵州|贵州]]、[[福建|福建]]等地，主要生活于竹林、草地、沼泽边、甘蔗田。该物种的模式产地在印度。<ref name='id1061'/>是血吸蟲(梭形裂体吸虫，''Schistosoma spindale''）的寄主。<ref name="Singh 1997">{{Cite journal 
| last1 = Inder Singh | first1 = K. 
| last2 = Krishnasamy | first2 = M. 
| last3 = Ambu | first3 = S. 
| last4 = Rasul | first4 = R. 
| last5 = Chong | first5 = N. L. 
| title = Studies on animal schistosomes in Peninsular Malaysia: Record of naturally infected animals and additional hosts of Schistosoma spindale 
| journal = The Southeast Asian journal of tropical medicine and public health 
